00:30:25,600 --> 00:30:26,600
Why?

463
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:27,600
Because we're fellowshipping, we're rejoicing.

464
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:31,400
That's what it's about.

465
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:39,040
And here, when I look at this passage, I think, man, that is what the work of God is all about.

466
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:43,440
Being invested and then rejoicing when we get to hear what God has done.

467
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:44,440
Let's pray together.

468
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,620
Father, we love you.

469
00:30:45,620 --> 00:30:47,120
We thank you so much for loving us.

470
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:50,960
We thank you, God, for your word and for the truth of your word.

471
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:55,000
We thank you for the part that we can have in missions.

472
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:59,840
God, I pray that you would prepare us this week spiritually.

473
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:07,320
Lord, that we would be in a place where we are ready for what you have for us.

474
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:10,760
I pray, God, that you would move and work, guide and direct.

475
00:31:10,760 --> 00:31:12,840
And we'll thank you for all that you'll do.

476
00:31:12,840 --> 00:31:14,840
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

477
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:15,340
Amen.

